OL,3,CFormer Wales full-back Liam Williams
OL,4,Cretires from rugby
OL,6,FFormer Wales and British and Irish
OL,7,FLions full-back Liam Williams has
OL,8,Fannounced his retirement from the game
OL,9,Fdue to ongoing knee problems.
OL,11,FWilliams, 34, who signed for Newcastle
OL,12,Fin September after leaving Saracens at
OL,13,Fthe end of last season, made 93
OL,14,Fappearances for Wales and five for the
OL,15,FLions during tours to New Zealand in
OL,16,F2017 and South Africa in 2021.
OL,18,FWilliams said in a post on social
OL,19,Fmedia: "I've been a professional for
OL,20,F15 years, that takes its toll.
