OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774576986
OL,3,CFormer Wales full-back Liam Williams
OL,4,Cretires from rugby
OL,6,F"I think it's the right time for me to
OL,7,Fcall it a day. I always thought I
OL,8,Fwould go out on my own terms. Having
OL,9,Fknee trouble for the past few years
OL,10,Fhas taken its toll.
OL,12,F"The feeling I have is one of immense
OL,13,Fpride."
OL,15,FWilliams, who scored 21 tries for
OL,16,FWales and helped them to two Six
OL,17,FNations titles, added: "Grateful for
OL,18,Fevery memory, and a thank you to
OL,19,Feveryone who backed me along the way.
